{"tid":356772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Android CDrom有福了] LHKGMaker 發佈","createTime":"2017-08-12T10:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T21:23:28.000Z","uid":133360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6deb0a310617c57a4deff24889c5534d9d0a899c","tid":356772,"uid":133360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"之前用app邀請碼轉過黎嘅全部都係蘋果狗<br />\n我實在睇唔過眼<br />\n於是<br />\n我用左幾個月時間，研究左個android app<br />\n可以拎個 <span style=\"color: violet;\"><del>邀請碼</del></span><br />\n至於個<del>邀請碼</del>有咩用途 我真係唔知<br />\n無人叫你拎個<del>邀請碼</del>黎註冊lihkg<br />\n<br />\nLink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ufile.io/ad12f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fufile.io%2Fad12f&d=20zEhBqoAHY0DZ7WuRoCz0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ff43fced\" target=\"_blank\">https://ufile.io/ad12f</a><br />\n限時下載一天<br />\n反應熱烈則再度上載<br />\n<br />\n個server無咁快開放住<br />\n請留意本post宣佈<br />\n<br />\n但爲左唔好重蹈覆轍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聲明：<br />\n本app與LIHKG (連登) 並無任何關連<br />\n本程式只爲個人練習及測試頻寬<br />\n並不會任何用於任何商業用途<br />\n及不會收集任何個人資料<br />\nUse at your own risk.<br />\n有任何問題本人恕不負責</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b5a074f8a0cc3463c5d171a2bb226f70678486","tid":356772,"uid":28354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"又撚狗？"},{"pid":"58833c820c2f06c8a8e7e164d1387ed8bc975699","tid":356772,"uid":133360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ae52b704ab9cdb0f31383423aea9eb0674191f","tid":356772,"uid":133360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又撚狗？</blockquote><br />\n你咪唔好信<br />\n得益既係cdrom"},{"pid":"37f29f79890bcd3041b88bf159600e99035b449b","tid":356772,"uid":133360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply